      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.415513,
      "replayEndSec": 9.087333,
      "narrationText": "第一个是 tunnel 命令。应用运行在服务器上，而不是你的笔记本上。隧道命令通过 SSH 转发容器端口，让你可以在浏览器中通过 localhost 访问它。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-01.458b6cf9.mp3",
      "textHash": "458b6cf9d8623b6ae88d667dce850ecb24cf2a58e2383d936ea93208c62401ef",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.027755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-01-after.1009a2bb.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.754286,
      "afterTextHash": "1009a2bb2a5696d8595a697de24f7f1c9c7b99b6138d3f5071ae6fb29b7d93fb"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-work-with-repo-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 9.087333,
      "replayEndSec": 15.893309,
      "narrationText": "第二个是 term 命令。终端连接命令让你进入仓库的沙盒内，视图与 VS Code 中看到的完全一样。无需离开终端，就能针对这个仓库的 Docker 守护进程运行任意命令。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-02.ab6fb7f4.mp3",
      "textHash": "ab6fb7f43f4e11dfde7e54c80f539daa526a0e055909fccd429284edd476d8ec",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.210612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-02-after.ee880c65.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.675918,
      "afterTextHash": "ee880c65f7dcef152d42c36fde40664e2f7c6235a994f8065c85502af19da258"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-work-with-repo-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 15.893309,
      "replayEndSec": 22.144638,
      "narrationText": "推送文件之前，先用 --dry-run 预览。它会显示将要变更的内容，而不实际复制任何东西。不确定时总是先预览。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-03.e27288f3.mp3",
      "textHash": "e27288f372065196a28e5f4e3104d1d38fbd022dbc2539e7c777effdbb8a8c78",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.684082,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-03-after.d1482552.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.004082,
      "afterTextHash": "d14825525f5032aa5d0fdebbb0a2a98e842d391d47f2186dc20dbd99d36d007b"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-work-with-repo-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 22.144638,
      "replayEndSec": 30.993341,
      "narrationText": "现在让我们正式执行上传。同步上传命令通过 SSH 将文件从笔记本移入仓库，使用 rsync 差量压缩。Tunnel、term、sync，三条命令覆盖日常循环。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-04.c756cb3d.mp3",
      "textHash": "c756cb3d7d09f350d3162e600b5b2be6c87859ce324622f268b48810af9e1c54",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.165714,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-04-after.da8e8030.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.362449,
      "afterTextHash": "da8e8030d8281871510d6613f7e183687d8691279c160f3c285535fce37b8ba1"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "97f216cbe96f549b228c4aab1e7c050e0fb4f777387d2ac45576f923404e7db3",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/intro.97f216cb.mp3",
      "narrationText": "好！你的应用已经在运行，那就让我们真正开始使用它。三条命令覆盖日常循环。",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.235918
    },
    {
      "id": "daily-three",
      "textHash": "ce33cf28d59116f93bde259eb29b8d3b1b73d8af4a846dad6380d3c7729f8e24",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/daily-three.ce33cf28.mp3",
      "narrationText": "tunnel 在浏览器中打开你的应用，term 在沙盒内运行命令，sync 在两端之间搬运文件。这就是日常的完整工作流。",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.389388
    },
    {
      "id": "open-tunnel",
      "textHash": "3614d6846d6f5cb8965ff12498de3820bd78c2fce15703e060d364cbf9ca0864",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-work-with-repo/open-tunnel.3614d684.mp3",
      "narrationText": "隧道运行时，应用会直接在您的浏览器中打开。在本演示中，我们加载 rediacc.com，就像访问从容器直接提供服务的自有应用一样。",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.322449
    },
